{"tid":2442614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"倒吊凌虐5歲女童逼喝尿　全身遭毆昏迷！心碎母盼人渣保母夫妻「下地獄」","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:55:29.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9695ca526b2abb59b8147384196c6c452c9a2e78","tid":2442614,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4rqxfOo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4rqxfOo.png&h=a05f912d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XbdS5pK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXbdS5pK.png&h=5de1e568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EtLgElv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEtLgElv.png&h=bcb03791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SCdjFF0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSCdjFF0.png&h=9e793369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜蘭縣一對沒有保母證照的夫妻檔，每個月收取2萬多元的保母費，受託照顧5歲的蘇姓女<br />\n童，卻凌虐女童，不僅對她拳打腳踢，甚至還扯頭髮、不給飯吃，甚至逼迫女童喝尿，或<br />\n是抓住她的雙腳倒立搖晃，讓飽受虐待的女童從胖胖可愛模樣，被折磨到不成人形，5日<br />\n深夜更昏迷、口吐白沫，這對無良夫妻檔才趕緊抱著女童送醫，但她的頭顱重創，經過醫<br />\n院緊急手術，才救回她性命，但是昏迷指數仍只有5至6分，需在加護病房觀察。<br />\n <br />\n宜蘭地方法院認定無良夫妻涉嫌《刑法》的傷害、凌虐妨害幼童發育罪，昨天（7日）凌<br />\n晨裁定曾姓保母與其許姓丈夫收押禁見，網友也對惡劣夫妻發出重怒與肉搜，《蘋果新聞<br />\n網》今天更獨家找到蘇姓女童的許姓生母，她痛批「真的很殘忍！」，還說「表面上跟我<br />\n好來好去，但私底下竟然是魔鬼」，盼司法重判這對夫妻檔，甚至還說「要讓她們下地獄<br />\n！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210308/FXPADRY5QBAGVBL6WBHE4U5XPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FFXPADRY5QBAGVBL6WBHE4U5XPM%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=58713a2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FFXPADRY5QBAGVBL6WBHE4U5XPM%2F&h=3e7cde1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210308/FXPADRY5QBAGVBL6WBHE4U5XPM/</a>"},{"pid":"6655461758cc4dac3972a34f3e52a53014375e4a","tid":2442614,"uid":264158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"屌 個保母心理變態<br />\n但我都好唔理解扔個5歲女俾陌生人湊係咩一回事"},{"pid":"930f6e67465dd7ee5548b6c28209fc8a6027884b","tid":2442614,"uid":229633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"咁可愛係點忍心落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627803dbee2cd2ecc4c6bdafa101495107d48d9d","tid":2442614,"uid":365791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b9e609f33fd4a6bc27aff5e661b89ee3a509fc","tid":2442614,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:16:02.000Z","msg":"以為係香港果單,,, 呢D虐兒者都真係應該落地獄"},{"pid":"64cf938bd33bc299fd7c9c78ef4676f2f68115d8","tid":2442614,"uid":172144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"寄宿？去到咁嚴重先揚出黎阿媽都十分疏忽下喎"}]}